videos.headline: King connects with Harris for 35-yard Miami TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King fakes a handoff and throws to Cam'Ron Harris, who trots into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (King connects with Harris for 35-yard Miami TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mallory stretches into end zone for Miami TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King makes a short pass to Will Mallory, who stretches across the goal line for a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mallory stretches into end zone for Miami TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harley spins into the end zone for Miami TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King throws a long pass to Mike Harley, who makes his way into the end zone for a 38-yard Hurricanes touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harley spins into the end zone for Miami TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams' interception sets up Pitt for short TD
videos.description: Marquis Williams intercepts D'Eriq King's pass and returns it 38 yards, setting up Pittsburgh for a one-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams' interception sets up Pitt for short TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt leaves Mallory wide open on 45-yard Miami TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King tosses the ball to Will Mallory, who darts into the end zone for a 45-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt leaves Mallory wide open on 45-yard Miami TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: D'Eriq King throws 4 TDs in Miami's win
videos.description: D'Eriq King tallies four total touchdown passes, leading Miami to a 31-19 win over Pittsburgh.
